message.body: Hey! Does it matter that my ipad is a mini?
Oh I don't know! I need to use iMovie. I'll check to make sure it's compatible with the mini
I might have to have you download iMovie from the App Store and I'll give you the money (it's 5 bucks)
Oh no problem!
I'm gonna charge you $10...ya know, gotta make a profit.
Gotta make that $$
I'm pretty sure the mini does everything the full size does...just looks cuter.
Yeah I think it's the same!
I have to get a dongle that hooks it to the projector.
I think I can borrow one from uarts
Mine has a stylish aztecian looking case too.
Does it have a little charger or a 30 pin charger?
Yeah, uarts probably has a ton of dongles just laying around.
Haha so many dongles here.
Hmmmm...not sure. Jules and I use the same charger.
I think it's the little guy. The older versions use the bigger one.
I'm pretty sure mine is little...I can show you this weekend!
I had plastic surgery yesterday.
Perfect!!! I want to make sure to get the right dongle, you know. Did you get a nose job?!?!
I got a labiaplasty...too many folds.
Jk I got the scar on my face stitched up.
I mean what are those folds even there for? Useless.
Totally useless.
How did it go?!
Are you in any pain?
You need me to bring you some Advil after work?
It was so quick and easy! My cheek is a little bruised and swollen, but I get my stitches out in a week and I should be good after that! :)
Just happy to have it done!
That's so great! You are gonna feel like a new person!
It doesn't hurt really...feels a little swollen, but that's all!
(Even though I never even noticed your scar, I know what it feels like to just know it's there)
I'm glad it went well!!
I wanna see your stitches
Oh you'll see them.
Yeah, it's been bothering me for years and made me feel bummed a lot of the time...glad it's gone!
#stitchface
#Frankenstein
Too bad it's not Halloween, I could have worked it into my costume!
Have a great day! KIT about Saturday! :)
Saturday is looking good so far!! Have a good day!
